# `TranscriptsFilters` Definition

| Property | Type | Required | Description |
|----------|------|----------|-------------|
| mediaType | `string` | No | The media type of the transcripts, default value is all  |
| startTimeMs | `number` | No | start time to filter by, default value is 7 days into the past |
| endTimeMs | `number` | No | end time to filter by, default value is current time |
| queues | `string[]` | No | list of queues ids to filter by |
| flows | `string[]` | No | list of flows ids to filter by |
